to keep my mouth shut.

47:29.250 --> 47:31.250
Like I said, I'm a friend.

47:31.958 --> 47:33.166
Police?

47:33.625 --> 47:34.833
Police?

47:35.333 --> 47:37.208
You want to call the police on me?

47:37.291 --> 47:39.500
