whoever you are.

47:39.791 --> 47:40.666
Are you listening?

47:40.750 --> 47:41.791
You can phone the police.

47:41.875 --> 47:44.750
There isn't a mother-fucking
cop in this whole place...

47:45.500 --> 47:46.958
...that doesn't have a price.

47:47.041 --> 47:48.958
You can ask Meyer.

47:49.958 --> 47:52.166
Whatever deal you had with him...

47:53.541 --> 47:54.750
Who?

47:55.125 --> 47:56.333
Meyer.

47:57.250 --> 47:58.750
Your friend.

47:59.750 --> 48:02.000
It's strange you don't know Meyer.

48:02.500 --> 48:03.458
Goodbye.

48:03.958 --> 48:05.500
You missing your carpet?

48:07.750 --> 48:10.125
I never said the cop was my friend.

48:12.833 --> 48:14.625
Four people in a room...

48:15.458 --> 48:16.833
One's dead.

48:17.958 --> 48:19.541
Here's the problem.

48:19.750 --> 48:22.375
How do you keep the
secret between the other three?

48:22.458 --> 48:24.875
After all, people talk.

48:28.083 --> 48:29.750
I know where the body is.

48:30.666 --> 48:32.791
I know you killed him.

48:33.166 --> 48:35.041
And I know about the guns.

48:49.958 --> 48:51.333
How much do you want?

48:53.750 --> 48:55.166
Hundred thousand.

48:55.958 --> 48:56.791
Hundred thousand Rand?

48:56.875 --> 48:59.166
Are you crazy?! That's a lot of money.

48:59.500 --> 49:01.208
Put the money in a duffel bag...

49:01.291 --> 49:03.666
...and drop it in the bins by Block E.

49:04.458 --> 49:05.791
Then walk away.

49:08.541 --> 49:10.166
I'll know if you're watching me.

49:14.375 --> 49:15.625
You still there?

49:16.125 --> 49:17.166
Yes.

49:20.458 --> 49:21.875
Bins by Block E.

49:21.958 --> 49:23.666
Tomorrow.

49:24.083 --> 49:26.291
I'll call you when it's time.

49:26.583 --> 49:28.333
You say you're a friend.

49:29.250 --> 49:31.958
Meyer also said he was a friend,
until he got too greedy.

49:32.250 --> 49:36.166
He became a greedy little pig.
And I don't like greedy little pigs.

49:36.625 --> 49:39.833
You're like a disease eating
away at my business.

49:40.791 --> 49:43.625
Are you a greedy little pig...

49:44.250 --> 49:45.333
...friend?

49:45.541 --> 49:48.750
Drop it in the bins and walk away.

50:05.500 --> 50:07.458
How are we going to pick up the money?

50:08.375 --> 50:11.000
I can't just walk over there and take it out.

50:11.500 --> 50:13.250
You won't.

50:13.500 --> 50:15.500
You'll already be in the bin waiting.

50:22.000 --> 50:23.708
- Listen asshole, do you think
I'm going to get in a dirty bin -

50:23.791 --> 50:25.125
- Watch yourself Warren.

50:26.333 --> 50:28.125
I might be in a wheelchair...

50:28.375 --> 50:30.250
...but don't mess with me.

50:34.458 --> 50:36.291
You asked for 50-50.

50:36.833 --> 50:38.458
So this is how you earn it.

50:41.250 --> 50:44.000
You didn't have to do that. I was just joking.

50:45.583 --> 50:47.250
But seriously...

50:48.541 --> 50:50.125
...does it have to be tomorrow?

50:58.041 --> 51:01.500
You know I wouldn't let
anything happen to you.

51:01.750 --> 51:02.833
Right?

51:06.958 --> 51:08.166
Baby?

51:10.625 --> 51:12.250
I'm going to beg my boss for a loan...

51:13.250 --> 51:14.625
...to pay Emmie back.

51:16.250 --> 51:18.375
Then we're done with this criminal shit.

51:26.375 --> 51:28.625
You'll get a normal job.

51:30.333 --> 51:32.083
Make honest money.

51:32.875 --> 51:34.958
We'll never be rich...

51:35.500 --> 51:36.750
...but we'll be happy.

51:37.375 --> 51:38.875
Can you do that?

51:46.625 --> 51:52.458
<i>I'm in da bins, da kids
knw wat 2 do. Ready</i>

52:17.625 --> 52:19.041
Bins by Block E.

52:19.375 --> 52:21.333
Drop it and walk away.

52:22.250 --> 52:23.541
Do it now.

52:54.750 --> 52:55.625
Oh yes.

54:25.041 --> 54:27.541
Come on boys.
You know what to do.

54:27.625 --> 54:30.291
Do what you need to do.

54:37.458 --> 54:39.250
There you go.

54:43.458 --> 54:44.500
Run!

55:37.458 --> 55:42.500
<i>Dd u get it?!!</i>

55:55.291 --> 55:57.500
