55:59.583 --> 56:00.666
And...

56:01.000 --> 56:03.250
...I made some good tips.

56:03.750 --> 56:05.750
I think we need to speak to Emmie.

56:05.833 --> 56:07.750
We can ask to pay him a bit at a time.

56:09.125 --> 56:10.875
I'm sure he'll understand.

56:11.750 --> 56:12.958
What do you think?

56:15.000 --> 56:16.041
What?

56:16.958 --> 56:18.375
What did you do?

56:19.333 --> 56:20.458
<i>- Come 2 window.</i>
- Randal?

56:23.291 --> 56:24.500
I...uhm...

56:26.000 --> 56:27.500
...I want to show you something.

56:29.625 --> 56:31.000
Come.

56:34.458 --> 56:36.250
<i>K @ window</i>

56:51.333 --> 56:52.625
What the fuck?

56:56.750 --> 56:58.750
Where did he get it?

57:17.000 --> 57:18.166
Randal?

57:18.583 --> 57:21.000
Tell me that's not Lawyer's money.

57:22.291 --> 57:23.875
You promised me!

57:26.291 --> 57:27.875
Do you realize what you've done?

57:28.041 --> 57:29.875
