57:30.083 --> 57:31.666
Oh my God, I can't believe...

57:31.750 --> 57:33.083
...you promised me!

57:33.166 --> 57:34.291
I had to do it.

57:34.375 --> 57:35.500
We've got the money.

57:35.750 --> 57:37.166
