Are you crazy?

57:37.250 --> 57:38.916
- It's not our money.
- We do have the money.

57:39.000 --> 57:40.625
Calm down. Calm down.

57:41.958 --> 57:43.583
I didn't have a choice.

57:44.291 --> 57:46.791
Emmie will kill us.

57:48.250 --> 57:49.875
He will.

58:05.375 --> 58:07.000
We're okay baby.

58:07.500 --> 58:09.833
We're alright. Promise.
Look there, we have the money.

58:13.250 --> 58:15.166
You're going to get us all killed.

58:15.250 --> 58:16.833
No I won't.

58:17.791 --> 58:19.375
I saved us.

58:34.250 --> 58:35.500
Okay.

58:35.833 --> 58:37.125
Now what?

58:43.958 --> 58:50.625
<i>Come round...We'll celebrate</i>

58:53.000 --> 58:54.666
<i>Why dnt u come round?</i>

58:54.750 --> 58:56.458
What's he saying?
When is he bringing it?

59:01.291 --> 59:07.750
<i>Lol. Seriously I want to feel it</i>

59:13.541 --> 59:16.375
<i>Nah, dnt grand walking</i>

59:21.750 --> 59:24.666
<i>Don't b a cunt.</i>

59:30.333 --> 59:31.625
<i>Fine. 70-30</i>

59:35.958 --> 59:37.416
<i>WTF?!</i>

59:37.500 --> 59:38.416
- Randal. Talk to me.

59:38.500 --> 59:40.333
- Randal. Talk to me.
- I did all da dirty wrk. I wnt more

1:00:01.375 --> 1:00:05.041
<i>K. 60-40. But she fetches it.
Or I'm gone with it all 2moro ;-)</i>

1:00:22.125 --> 1:00:23.958
He wants you to go fetch it.

1:00:28.041 --> 1:00:29.458
Why does he want you to fetch it?

1:00:29.750 --> 1:00:30.583
What?

1:00:30.666 --> 1:00:33.041
Why does he want you to fetch it?

1:00:33.125 --> 1:00:35.083
I've been watching you two for a while.

1:00:35.791 --> 1:00:37.166
I'm not stupid.

1:00:37.250 --> 1:00:38.166
Is this a joke?

1:00:38.250 --> 1:00:40.458
Don't talk shit to me.

1:00:40.958 --> 1:00:42.208
What's going on between you two?

1:00:42.291 --> 1:00:43.125
Are you serious?

1:00:43.208 --> 1:00:44.041
Yes. I'm serious.

1:00:44.125 --> 1:00:45.166
You're full of shit.

1:00:45.583 --> 1:00:46.500
Pam!

1:00:53.333 --> 1:00:54.250
Pam!

1:01:01.125 --> 1:01:02.041
Pam!

1:01:04.041 --> 1:01:07.333
Hey, shut the hell up man!

1:01:28.458 --> 1:01:33.750
<i>I'm sorry.</i>

1:04:40.458 --> 1:04:41.958
Do you think it's gonna rain?

1:04:54.833 --> 1:04:56.291
Are you gonna ask?

1:04:58.791 --> 1:05:00.125
Ask what?

1:05:01.958 --> 1:05:03.791
What happened with me and Warren.

1:05:09.041 --> 1:05:10.458
No.

1:05:17.250 --> 1:05:19.583
We're in hell and we
don't even know it.

1:05:22.291 --> 1:05:24.958
Money, money, money, money.

1:05:26.291 --> 1:05:29.250
Money is the devil we keep
chasing in the hope of something better.

1:05:30.875 --> 1:05:32.083
But actually...

1:05:33.833 --> 1:05:36.583
...actually we're all chained to it.

1:06:03.125 --> 1:06:04.375
Okay.

1:06:05.250 --> 1:06:06.750
I'll be right back.

1:07:51.750 --> 1:07:53.333
We'll go in while he's away.

1:07:55.958 --> 1:07:57.875
You mean break in.

1:08:04.625 --> 1:08:07.041
We could always just pop Emmie.

1:08:19.958 --> 1:08:23.958
<i>Cum luk at my new ride.</i>

1:08:27.750 --> 1:08:28.958
What the hell.

1:08:43.333 --> 1:08:45.125
This guy's an idiot.

1:09:10.875 --> 1:09:12.541
He's gonna get us all killed!

1:09:19.375 --> 1:09:21.791
<i>I like it when you call me Big Poppa.</i>

1:09:21.875 --> 1:09:23.250
Yo bitch!

1:09:23.333 --> 1:09:25.166
What the hell are you doing?

1:09:25.250 --> 1:09:27.250
By the way. Check out my jacket.
You like it?

1:09:27.458 --> 1:09:28.875
Are you stupid?

1:09:28.958 --> 1:09:30.666
Are you trying to get us all killed?

1:09:30.750 --> 1:09:33.458
What I do with my money
is my business.

1:09:33.541 --> 1:09:35.125
You got your share.

1:09:36.000 --> 1:09:37.291
Where're they going?

1:09:53.541 --> 1:09:54.458
Randal...

1:09:54.625 --> 1:09:55.958
...something’s up.

1:10:08.958 --> 1:10:11.458
C'mon, c'mon, c'mon!
Pick up your phone!

1:10:12.291 --> 1:10:13.500
Warren.

1:10:14.083 --> 1:10:15.125
C'mon!

1:10:23.291 --> 1:10:24.541
Why's he not picking up?

1:10:29.041 --> 1:10:30.250
Randal.

1:10:30.541 --> 1:10:31.750
They're gonna kill him.

1:10:36.041 --> 1:10:37.333
Stop it.

1:10:39.458 --> 1:10:40.750
Stop it.

1:10:41.250 --> 1:10:42.250
Warren!

1:10:46.000 --> 1:10:47.000
Stop.

1:10:47.750 --> 1:10:48.833
Run.

1:10:49.750 --> 1:10:50.750
Run, Warren.

1:11:39.458 --> 1:11:41.250
We should've gone to the police -

1:12:19.166 --> 1:12:20.333
Randal Hendricks?

1:12:21.666 --> 1:12:23.291
Lieutenant-Colonel Gail February.

1:12:23.375 --> 1:12:24.875
I have a few questions for you.

1:12:26.083 --> 1:12:27.333
May I come in?

1:12:39.375 --> 1:12:40.750
Your wife?

1:12:41.583 --> 1:12:43.458
Girlfriend. She's not here right now.

1:12:44.166 --> 1:12:45.375
You're here about Warren.

1:12:46.083 --> 1:12:48.458
Can you think of anyone
who would want him dead?

1:12:54.541 --> 1:12:56.625
Mr. Hendricks, I'm not going
to beat around the bush.

1:12:58.958 --> 1:13:02.750
You called Warren just before he died
and you had a brief conversation.

1:13:03.333 --> 1:13:05.416
You called again a few minutes later...

1:13:05.500 --> 1:13:07.083
...but he didn't answer.

1:13:08.250 --> 1:13:12.083
Presumably because he was
being murdered at the time.

1:13:13.000 --> 1:13:14.583
Is there a question there?

1:13:15.041 --> 1:13:16.291
What did you talk about?

1:13:17.375 --> 1:13:20.583
I told him to come around for supper.
I can't exactly go to him.

1:13:22.541 --> 1:13:23.791
Hobby?

1:13:24.083 --> 1:13:27.250
My girlfriend got it for me. I like pigeons.

1:13:32.958 --> 1:13:34.083
Come to window.

1:13:34.666 --> 1:13:36.250
Okay at window.

1:13:36.791 --> 1:13:38.625
Come around. We can celebrate.

1:13:39.250 --> 1:13:40.750
Why don't you come around?

1:13:41.375 --> 1:13:43.958
Laugh out loud. Seriously I want to feel it!

1:13:44.958 --> 1:13:46.458
Nah I don't feel like walking.

1:13:46.958 --> 1:13:48.250
Hey don't be a cu...

1:13:50.291 --> 1:13:52.458
It gets pretty heated towards the end.

1:13:53.583 --> 1:13:55.583
Want to tell me what
you were talking about?

1:13:56.000 --> 1:13:57.666
Am I a suspect Lieutenant?

1:14:10.166 --> 1:14:12.250
Have you seen him before?

1:14:13.250 --> 1:14:15.458
My partner, Lieutenant-Colonel Meyer.

1:14:22.541 --> 1:14:24.458
Sorry I've never seen him before.

1:14:30.000 --> 1:14:31.958
Thanks for your time, Mr. Hendricks.

1:14:33.083 --> 1:14:35.458
If you think of anything...

1:14:38.041 --> 1:14:39.250
...call me.

1:14:42.125 --> 1:14:43.541
You're not from around here, are you?

1:14:44.666 --> 1:14:46.500
We don't call the police here.

1:14:46.833 --> 1:14:47.875
Know why?

1:14:48.791 --> 1:14:50.666
You're all just as bad as us.

1:14:51.125 --> 1:14:52.333
Not all of us.

1:15:04.458 --> 1:15:06.458
That guy Randal knows
more than he's letting on.

1:15:06.541 --> 1:15:07.375
Is it?

1:15:08.333 --> 1:15:09.916
When I showed him Meyer's picture...

1:15:10.000 --> 1:15:12.750
- I could see he knows something.
- Gail.

1:15:13.833 --> 1:15:16.250
Pastor White. Uhm...thanks.

1:15:22.250 --> 1:15:24.291
I've done something.

1:15:27.791 --> 1:15:29.458
I've done something terrible.

1:15:44.541 --> 1:15:45.458
Here.

1:15:45.625 --> 1:15:46.833
Time's up.

1:15:51.250 --> 1:15:52.166
Come on.

1:16:01.750 --> 1:16:04.250
Shit, I forgot Lindsey's money.

1:16:04.333 --> 1:16:05.208
It's alright I'll get it.

1:16:05.291 --> 1:16:07.375
Go down so long and get someone
to help me down the stairs.

1:16:07.458 --> 1:16:08.750
Hurry.

1:16:41.625 --> 1:16:43.500
Lost something?

1:16:55.041 --> 1:16:57.458
Going somewhere Pam?

1:16:58.500 --> 1:17:00.250
Emmie, just listen to...

1:17:07.375 --> 1:17:08.666
- Emmie...hear me out...

1:17:08.750 --> 1:17:10.041
- Emmie...hear me out...
- So...

1:17:10.500 --> 1:17:12.416
...where’s my money, hmm?

1:17:12.500 --> 1:17:13.791
We will get it for you, bra...

1:17:27.541 --> 1:17:29.000
Bastard!
- Where's my damn money?

1:17:29.083 --> 1:17:29.958
- Where's my damn money?
- We got it.

1:17:30.291 --> 1:17:31.375
We got it.

1:17:36.041 --> 1:17:37.041
So...

1:17:37.958 --> 1:17:39.166
...go get it.

1:17:44.375 --> 1:17:45.625
Our friend has it.

1:17:45.958 --> 1:17:47.166
We did a job.

1:17:49.250 --> 1:17:50.625
What kind of job was it Pam?

1:17:50.958 --> 1:17:52.875
Emmie, there's police everywhere.

1:17:52.958 --> 1:17:53.875
Just give us a chance please.

1:17:53.958 --> 1:17:54.791
Emmie.

1:17:54.875 --> 1:17:56.958
We were going to fetch
it earlier but then uhm...

1:17:57.958 --> 1:18:00.000
...but there was a shoot-out.
And we couldn't get it.

1:18:00.958 --> 1:18:02.375
We can get it tomorrow.

1:18:03.000 --> 1:18:04.333
Just one day.

1:18:05.791 --> 1:18:07.250
One day is all I'm asking for.

1:18:07.333 --> 1:18:09.458
Just one day. Just one day. Just one day.

1:18:11.583 --> 1:18:14.458
Please man, I'm begging you, please...

1:18:20.000 --> 1:18:21.000
Okay.

1:18:25.458 --> 1:18:26.458
Right.

1:18:30.583 --> 1:18:31.958
Until tomorrow then.

1:18:37.083 --> 1:18:38.458
But I...

1:18:39.250 --> 1:18:41.125
...need something in return.

1:18:44.666 --> 1:18:46.750
Call it interest if you will.

1:19:08.791 --> 1:19:10.125
Pam.

1:19:10.666 --> 1:19:12.000
Pam.

1:20:08.583 --> 1:20:10.291
What're we gonna do?

1:20:12.625 --> 1:20:14.625
I know you have no reason to trust me.

1:20:16.541 --> 1:20:18.500
But just give me one more chance.

1:20:19.833 --> 1:20:22.458
Just one more chance.
That's all I'm asking for.

1:20:36.375 --> 1:20:42.041
Every plan I've ever made has landed
us in deeper and deeper trouble.

1:20:44.166 --> 1:20:46.958
There was a time when
I could protect you.

1:20:48.250 --> 1:20:49.750
But not anymore.

1:20:51.666 --> 1:20:53.250
