1:21:10.250 --> 1:21:11.666
You can't go.

1:21:14.750 --> 1:21:16.750
Not in your wheelchair.

1:21:18.458 --> 1:21:20.291
We need help.

1:21:30.333 --> 1:21:32.166
Right. Now put the shank...

1:21:33.041 --> 1:21:35.333
