1:22:18.458 --> 1:22:19.375
Again.

1:22:23.250 --> 1:22:24.458
You ready?

1:22:31.958 --> 1:22:32.958
Wait...

1:22:33.250 --> 1:22:34.750
I need to make it right.

1:22:35.250 --> 1:22:38.041
But first I have to get rid of Emmie.

1:22:46.791 --> 1:22:48.333
Detective February.

1:22:49.541 --> 1:22:51.416
It's Randal Hendricks.

1:22:51.500 --> 1:22:52.958
I'm ready to talk.

1:22:54.625 --> 1:22:56.250
Okay. Just hold on.

1:23:03.833 --> 1:23:05.291
Alright.

1:23:05.750 --> 1:23:08.500
I'm sure you know your
partner's dead Detective.

1:23:10.000 --> 1:23:11.958
I saw it with my binoculars.

1:23:13.500 --> 1:23:14.958
Your partner was dirty.

1:23:16.000 --> 1:23:17.333
Are you?

1:23:19.458 --> 1:23:21.166
I'm not my partner.

1:23:22.250 --> 1:23:24.041
I wish you were.

1:23:25.125 --> 1:23:28.041
You would've stood a better
chance at that police station.

1:23:29.041 --> 1:23:30.958
Warren...

1:23:33.000 --> 1:23:35.791
Warren and I decided to blackmail Lawyer.

1:23:41.458 --> 1:23:44.791
If I bring him in, will you testify?

1:23:45.125 --> 1:23:47.958
Yes but if they find out I said
something they'll kill my...

1:23:52.250 --> 1:23:55.833
Arrest me, Detective.
Use me, whatever.

1:23:57.750 --> 1:23:59.166
But my girlfriend...

1:24:00.125 --> 1:24:01.750
I give you my word.

1:24:02.666 --> 1:24:04.541
I'll protect you both.

1:24:12.958 --> 1:24:14.291
Who the hell is that?

1:24:14.375 --> 1:24:15.750
Go see who it is.

1:24:37.083 --> 1:24:38.750
I come in peace.

1:25:05.750 --> 1:25:08.250
I'll be watching you the whole time.

1:25:21.458 --> 1:25:22.875
Randal?

1:25:23.833 --> 1:25:25.250
Nothing happened.

1:25:26.458 --> 1:25:28.583
He made his move...

1:25:29.583 --> 1:25:31.291
...I told him he's an asshole.

1:25:32.375 --> 1:25:33.625
We laughed...

1:25:34.541 --> 1:25:36.083
...smoked...

1:25:37.000 --> 1:25:38.500
...then I cried and...

1:25:40.875 --> 1:25:42.833
...told him you're a bitch.

1:26:02.041 --> 1:26:03.500
I love you.

1:26:05.333 --> 1:26:06.875
You're full of crap...

1:26:10.625 --> 1:26:12.458
...but I love you.

1:27:13.291 --> 1:27:14.541
You there yet?

1:27:14.625 --> 1:27:15.958
Almost.

1:27:17.958 --> 1:27:19.583
Okay, I'm here.

1:27:19.666 --> 1:27:21.500
Number 37.

1:27:31.958 --> 1:27:34.250
Right, remember. Just like we practiced.

1:27:35.125 --> 1:27:36.833
Feel for the pins.

1:27:40.791 --> 1:27:41.958
Can you feel them?

1:27:42.041 --> 1:27:44.083
Yes, but the last one is stuck.

1:27:44.791 --> 1:27:47.708
Put more pressure on it.
Try to turn the shank.

1:27:47.791 --> 1:27:49.083
Hurry-up Pam.

1:27:49.166 --> 1:27:51.375
I know. Wait.

1:27:51.458 --> 1:27:52.625
Pam?

1:27:53.083 --> 1:27:54.250
Pam?

1:28:18.875 --> 1:28:20.250
Where are you?

1:28:29.666 --> 1:28:31.000
Shit.

1:28:34.250 --> 1:28:36.958
Shit Pam, is your phone on silent or not?

1:28:55.583 --> 1:28:59.375
Pam, Spook is there.
Run now. Now, now, now. Run.

1:28:59.458 --> 1:29:01.541
Hide Pam. Now!

1:29:07.833 --> 1:29:08.750
Pam?

1:29:09.541 --> 1:29:10.541
Pam?!

1:29:28.458 --> 1:29:31.083
Let's talk about Detective Meyer.

1:29:34.125 --> 1:29:37.375
I admire your commitment to the law lady.

1:29:37.458 --> 1:29:39.458
But let me tell you something.
On the Cape Flats...

1:29:39.541 --> 1:29:41.250
...it's misplaced.

1:29:41.750 --> 1:29:45.250
Where were you yesterday
between 7am and 2pm?

1:29:46.000 --> 1:29:47.458
I was sleeping.

1:29:48.625 --> 1:29:50.666
And yesterday during the shooting?

1:29:50.958 --> 1:29:52.458
Shooting?

1:29:53.041 --> 1:29:55.125
People shoot the whole
day on the Cape Flats.

1:29:55.375 --> 1:29:56.500
Detective.

1:29:56.750 --> 1:29:58.041
A word please.

1:30:08.375 --> 1:30:12.250
Can someone take these damn things off me.

1:30:22.041 --> 1:30:24.375
They're fighting about something.

1:30:25.625 --> 1:30:26.458
Shit.

1:30:26.541 --> 1:30:27.416
What?

1:30:27.500 --> 1:30:29.250
Nothing. Don't worry about it.

1:30:29.333 --> 1:30:30.666
What's going on?

1:30:30.750 --> 1:30:31.833
I can't hear anything.

1:30:33.125 --> 1:30:35.083
Pam, he's coming to the room.

1:31:11.666 --> 1:31:14.083
He's back in the lounge.

1:31:43.625 --> 1:31:44.958
What's going on? What is it?

1:31:47.958 --> 1:31:50.458
No. Stay there. Just stay there.

1:32:01.958 --> 1:32:03.250
Release him.

1:32:48.333 --> 1:32:49.916
Don't even think about it.

1:32:50.000 --> 1:32:51.750
Relax.

1:32:56.875 --> 1:32:58.333
On the table.

1:33:02.583 --> 1:33:04.541
Ever shot a man before?

1:33:10.583 --> 1:33:12.083
I don't think so.

1:33:34.750 --> 1:33:36.250
Stupid bitch!

1:34:07.791 --> 1:34:10.083
Jeez girl.

1:34:58.958 --> 1:35:00.458
No, please!

1:35:43.500 --> 1:35:45.250
What did I tell you...

1:35:45.750 --> 1:35:48.166
...about greedy little pigs?

1:35:48.250 --> 1:35:49.458
Randal!

1:35:49.541 --> 1:35:51.375
No, stop it!

1:35:51.625 --> 1:35:52.666
Let her go.

1:35:52.750 --> 1:35:54.416
Please! Leave her alone.

1:35:54.500 --> 1:35:57.000
I'm begging you. Please.

1:35:57.583 --> 1:35:59.166
Please just let her go!

1:35:59.250 --> 1:36:01.375
Bye Randal.

1:36:01.458 --> 1:36:03.333
Randal!

1:36:19.666 --> 1:36:22.291
Answer the bloody phone, Randal.

1:37:03.333 --> 1:37:04.541
Mrs. Raymond.

1:37:54.250 --> 1:37:55.375
Emmie!

1:37:57.291 --> 1:37:58.875
The door's open!

1:38:24.291 --> 1:38:25.875
Randal?

1:38:26.875 --> 1:38:28.250
Pam?

1:38:40.458 --> 1:38:43.958
Yes you, you're gonna learn.

1:38:53.958 --> 1:38:55.458
They ran.

1:38:56.250 --> 1:38:57.750
The assholes.

1:39:17.750 --> 1:39:18.958
Pam?

1:39:19.041 --> 1:39:20.750
Where are you?

1:39:22.375 --> 1:39:24.250
Pam, can't talk right now...

1:39:26.083 --> 1:39:27.458
...Randal.

1:39:27.666 --> 1:39:29.375
This isn't Randal.

1:39:29.750 --> 1:39:31.000
Are you sure?

1:39:31.875 --> 1:39:33.875
After you worked so
hard to get your money.

1:39:33.958 --> 1:39:35.750
I've got it right here.

1:39:38.666 --> 1:39:40.500
So you're the rubbish with my money.

1:39:42.583 --> 1:39:45.791
Bring it here. I'm waiting for you.

1:39:51.250 --> 1:39:52.958
The motherfucker.

1:39:53.541 --> 1:39:54.791
He doesn't know
who he's dealing with.

1:39:57.250 --> 1:39:59.625
Hey bra. Lawyer, check this out.

1:40:00.166 --> 1:40:03.041
I told you it's a bunch
of nutcases in this block.

1:40:13.750 --> 1:40:15.125
Tell me...

1:40:15.458 --> 1:40:17.541
...in which one of these apartments...

1:40:18.458 --> 1:40:19.833
...does Randal stay?

1:40:29.166 --> 1:40:30.750
He stays down there.

1:40:32.166 --> 1:40:33.583
There where the door is open.

1:40:52.833 --> 1:40:55.458
Help the poor man into his wheelchair.

1:40:55.750 --> 1:40:57.458
Seriously?

1:41:04.458 --> 1:41:06.291
Now I must do this crap.

1:41:12.625 --> 1:41:14.000
Then you're still heavy also.

1:41:14.625 --> 1:41:15.791
You must learn to walk now.

1:41:25.500 --> 1:41:26.916
What kind of man...

1:41:27.000 --> 1:41:28.291
...sends his woman...

1:41:28.375 --> 1:41:30.083
...to do his dirty work?

1:41:38.625 --> 1:41:39.875
Where's Pam?

1:41:39.958 --> 1:41:40.875
Pam?

1:41:40.958 --> 1:41:43.041
She's a bit tied up at the moment.

1:41:46.791 --> 1:41:48.083
Is that for me?

1:41:49.083 --> 1:41:50.083
A little present.

1:41:50.166 --> 1:41:52.541
An example of what happens to people...

1:41:53.291 --> 1:41:55.000
...that think they can steal from me.

1:42:00.666 --> 1:42:02.291
Hey you.

1:42:02.375 --> 1:42:04.125
Relax.

1:42:10.083 --> 1:42:11.500
Gentlemen...

1:42:13.083 --> 1:42:14.750
...put the guns down.

1:42:15.750 --> 1:42:17.125
Just give me the money.

1:42:17.375 --> 1:42:19.166
Why don't you go ask Pam...

1:42:19.458 --> 1:42:21.000
...what happens to pigs...

1:42:21.083 --> 1:42:22.375
...that think they can steal from me.

1:42:22.458 --> 1:42:23.375
Hey!

1:42:23.458 --> 1:42:25.958
They stole from me.

1:42:26.291 --> 1:42:28.250
I just want what's mine.

1:42:29.291 --> 1:42:30.291
If you say so.

1:42:30.750 --> 1:42:32.833
If you, say so.

1:42:57.875 --> 1:43:00.666
<i>10-35. Gun shots reported
in Haven Mansions.</i>

1:43:00.750 --> 1:43:04.625
<i>All units requested to respond.
Be extremely careful.</i>

1:43:05.625 --> 1:43:08.125
<i>B-23. 10-4. On route.</i>

1:43:12.375 --> 1:43:14.000
<i>A-24. 10-20.</i>

1:43:16.250 --> 1:43:17.750
C'mon Randal.

1:43:19.041 --> 1:43:21.166
C'mon answer the phone.

1:44:20.666 --> 1:44:22.125
Mother...

1:44:22.833 --> 1:44:24.000
...fucker.

1:45:09.958 --> 1:45:12.833
So Lieutenant-Colonel,
what do you make of this?

1:45:18.041 --> 1:45:19.958
I had him in custody.

1:45:26.250 --> 1:45:28.458
We know who they are,
but who are these two?

1:45:32.250 --> 1:45:33.791
The people who live here,
the ones in the photos...

1:45:35.666 --> 1:45:37.166
...they must know something.

1:45:37.250 --> 1:45:39.458
We need to find them.

1:45:48.875 --> 1:45:51.333
Lieutenant I asked you a question.

1:45:53.041 --> 1:45:54.833
Hey! I'm talking to you.

1:45:57.750 --> 1:46:00.166
The people who live here.
We need to find them.

1:46:00.250 --> 1:46:01.750
Do you know who they are?

1:46:11.750 --> 1:46:12.583
No sir.

1:47:11.750 --> 1:47:12.958
I'm okay.

1:47:14.458 --> 1:47:15.583
I'm okay.

1:47:16.375 --> 1:47:18.083
Pam.
